text: min anounhnhate aoy anak( mou ham meat) riebkear cheamuoy sdrei dtei banteabpi noh laey haeyka min ach phlasabdaur puok neang tow yk phriyea phe sa ng ban der tohbeicha samrosa robsa puokke teakteanh anak yeangnakadaoy leuklengte khnhom bamreu srei dachthlai robsa anak bonnaoh . haey a l laoh kuchea anak theroksaa krobkrong leu avei teangoasa
